12  public class HolderFactoryImpl<T extends Collection> implements HolderFactory<T> {
13      protected Class<T> holerCollection;
14  
15      public HolderFactoryImpl( Class<T> holerCollection ) {
16          this.holerCollection = holerCollection;
17      }
18  
19      @Override
20      public <Q> Holder<Q> build() {
21          return new HolderImpl( Objects2.newInstance( holerCollection ) );
22      }
23  }
